<script type="text/javascript">    
    // Can also be used with $(document).ready()
    var j8 = jQuery.noConflict();
    j8(window).load(function() {
        j8('.flexslider-8-1').flexslider({
            animation: "fade",
            controlNav: "thumbnails",
            slideshowSpeed: 5000,
            minItems: 2,
            maxItems: 4,
            start : function() {

                
                var sizeThumbs = jQuery('.flex-control-thumbs').children().size();
                var right = 145;
                jQuery('.slides li a p span').css('right', ((sizeThumbs * 60) + right) + 'px');

                var list = jQuery('.flex-control-thumbs');
                var listItems = list.children('li');
                list.append(listItems.get().reverse());
            }
        });
    });
</script>

        });

        function bannerClicks(id_banner, id_slider){
        click_url = 'http://www.somlivre.com/bannerslider/index/click/';
        banner_id = id_banner;
        new Ajax.Request(click_url,{
            method: 'post',
            parameters:{id_banner: banner_id, slider_id:id_slider},
            onFailure: '',
            onSuccess: ''
            
        });
        
    }

            Event.observe(window, 'load', function() {

                banner_ids = '1,2,3,4,5,6,7,8';

                slider_id = '1';

                    method: 'post',

                    parameters:{banner_ids: banner_ids, slider_id:slider_id},

                    onFailure: '',

                    onSuccess: ''



                });

            });

        var freeProductsCheckFlag = false;
        var selectAllfreeProducts = function(txt){
            if (freeProductsCheckFlag == false) {
                $$('.free-product-checkbox').each(function(elem){
                    elem.checked = true;
                });
                freeProductsCheckFlag = true;
                txt.innerHTML= "desmarcar todos";
            } else {
                $$('.free-product-checkbox').each(function(elem){
                    elem.checked = false;
                });
                freeProductsCheckFlag = false;
                txt.innerHTML= "marcar todos";
            }
        }

        var initForm = function() {
            var freeProductToCartForm = new VarienForm('free-product-form');
            freeProductToCartForm.submit = function(){
                if (this.validator.validate()) {
                    this.form.submit();
                }
            }.bind(freeProductToCartForm);
            return freeProductToCartForm;
        }
    </script>

<script>
function openChat(){
	var pageURL = document.URL;

	var pattern = new RegExp('.\/shop\/IT\/.','i');
	var equiPattern=new RegExp('.\/shop\/equipment\/en-us\/.','i');
      	if(pageURL.match(pattern)){

             window.open('https://cim.pb.com/netagent/cimlogin.aspx?questid=B28792A7-9D1A-4F67-93EF-877B3B2F164B&portid=F4412732-32E1-41C8-BF5D-228D36393712&loginname=Online%20Store%20User&subject=OnlineStore_Service&nareferer='+escape(document.location),'_blank','resizable= no,width=700,height=475,scrollbars=yes');
	}else if(pageURL.match(equiPattern)){

	      window.open('https://cim.pb.com/netagent/cimlogin.aspx?questid=9721EE1E-51BF-4C73-8BB4-6FA769A5A5EE&portid=82D75409-05C4-4165-A2EE-868B06D25928&nareferer=http%3A//www.pitneybowes.com/us/shipping-and-mailing/postage-meters/mailstation-2-mailing-system.html','_blank','resizable= no,width=900,height=475');
	}
	else{

	      window.open('https://cim.pb.com/netagent/cimlogin.aspx?questid=B28792A7-9D1A-4F67-93EF-877B3B2F164B&portid=9E049961-23FE-4FA1-BECC-38DD4BF117BC&loginname=Online%20Store%20User&subject=OnlineStore_Service&nareferer='+escape(document.location),'_blank','resizable= no,width=900,height=475');
	}
	return false;
}
</script>

<script>
function sendEvent(event, partNumber,product){
var Product  = product;
var product1 = null;
var product2 = null;
var productName = null;
var d_quote_test	=	product.indexOf("d_quotes");
var s_quote_test	=	product.indexOf("s_quotes");
if (d_quote_test > -1){
product2 = Product.replace('d_quotes', '"');
productName = product2;
}
else if (s_quote_test > -1){
product1 = Product.replace("s_quotes", "'");
productName = product1;
}
else{
productName = Product;
}

DDO.eventData = {     
 "action"     :event,
 "productID"  :partNumber,
 "productName":productName 	
}
 _satellite.track('sendEvent');

}

}
 _satellite.track('sendEvent');

}
 _satellite.track('sendEvent');
